              <text>Section 29(1) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">a person who has not attained the age of 18 years and who has never married or entered into a civil union (in subsection (3) of this section referred to as the child)</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">an eligible child (the <emphasis style="bold">child</emphasis>)</amend.in>.</text>
