                  <para>
                    <text><changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">Sections <struckoutwords amend.level1="struckout-cowh">73, 74, and 74A</struckoutwords> <insertwords amend.level1="insert-cowh">74 and 75</insertwords></citation></changeable> apply to information provided by the Registrar under subsection (5).</text>
