            <text>Section 16A(4)(b): omit <amend.in quote="1">Births, Deaths, and Marriages Registration Act 1995</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Registration Act 1995</amend.in>.</text>
