                </para>
              </def-para>
            </amend>
            <follow-text space-before="no">.</follow-text>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Definition of <def-term id="DLM1049039">the Act</def-term> in subclause (1): omit <amend.in quote="1">Births, Deaths, and Marriages Registration Act 1995</amend.in> and substitute <amend.in quote="1">Births, Deaths, Marriages, and Relationships Registration Act 1995</amend.in>.</text>
